<html>
  <head>
    <title>
      <%=  "Your Yoga Today Subscription has been cancelled." %>
    </title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= render :partial => "shared/email_header2",
      :locals => { :headertitle => "Your Yoga Today Subscription has been cancelled." } %>
    <div>
      <br />
      Hello <%= @user.name %> ,
      <br />
      <p>
      This message is to confirm your request to cancel your Yoga Today subscription.
      Your account has been removed from our billing database and you will no longer
      be charged the recurring subscription fee.</p>
      <br />

      <p>
      Final Charge and Date: <%= number_to_currency(@last_payment.amount) %> on <%= @last_payment.created_at.to_s(:long_day).squeeze(' ') %>
      </p>

      <br />
      <p>
      Your Unlimited access to the Yoga Today Library will continue until the end of the term you have purchased.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
      Current Term: Valid through <%= @subscription.next_renewal_at.to_s(:long_day).squeeze(' ') %>.
      </p>
      <br />

      <p>To reactivate your subscription, <%= link_to "Click Here", billing_user_url(@user) %></p>
      <br />
      <p>
      To let us know how we could have done better, please send a note to
      suggestions@yogatoday.com.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
      Thanks for being a part of the Yoga Today Community. We're sad to see you go and hope you'll be back someday.
      </p>
      <br />
      Namaste :)
      <br />
      <p>
      For details about the Yoga Today Terms of Service, visit
      <a href="http://www.yogatoday.com/terms-and-conditions">
        http://www.yogatoday.com/terms-and-conditions
      </a>
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
      If you require further assistance, please contact support@yogatoday.com
      </p>
      <br />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

